please use the corresponding binding parameter <code>sumOnTop</code> instead.

Example: <pre>
  oTable.bindRows({
     path: "...",
     parameters: {
        sumOnTop: true
     }
  });
</pre>

The value of the property is only taken into account if no parameter is given in the binding information. Changes to this property after the table is bound do not have any effect unless an explicit (re-)bind of the <code>rows</code> aggregation is done.

